        <entry xml:id="AOHenley_anonymousweather-idp350400">
          <form>
            <orth>[earrach]</orth>
          </form>
          <def>“Mios faoillaich, naoi latha gearran, trì latha sguabaig, suas an t-earrach.” Used to herald the beginning of spring.</def>
